# Production-Ready 3-Tier Kubernetes Chat Application

A scalable, containerized 3-tier chat application orchestrated inside a Kubernetes cluster. This project demonstrates microservices architecture, internal service discovery, traffic routing via an Ingress controller, and persistent data storage.

## Architecture Overview

The system is separated into three distinct layers to ensure isolation, independent scalability, and security:

1. **Frontend Tier:** Web UI container running behind a Kubernetes Service.
2. **Backend Tier:** Node.js/Express API handling core business logic, real-time messaging, and database operations.
3. **Database Tier:** A stateful MongoDB instance running cluster-internal to manage user data and chat history.
4. **Traffic Management:** A Kubernetes Ingress Controller routes external internet traffic safely to the frontend service.

