## Tech Stack & Tools

- **Orchestration:** Kubernetes (k8s)
- **Containerization:** Docker
- **Frontend:** Node.js (Web UI Layer)
- **Backend:** Node.js / Express
- **Database:** MongoDB
- **Networking:** Kubernetes Services (ClusterIP), Ingress Controller, CoreDNS

